				<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="544">
					<tr valign="top">
						<td width="10" class="o">*</td>
						<td class="o"> As a fish in the family of stingray, skate tastes sweet. It is a high-protein, low-fat food and rich in such minerals as calcium and iron. The pungent and sharp taste of skate comes from the nitrogenous compounds such as urea, ammonia, and trimethylamine</td>
					</tr>					
					<tr><td><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="20" border="0"></td></tr>
