						<td class="o"> 
							Seasoning: soy sauce 2 Tbsp, water 4 Tbsp, starch syrup 2 Tbsp, onion juice 2 Tbsp, cooking wine 1 Tbsp, garlic  Tbsp, black pepper 1 tsp, grape wine 1<br> 
							Tbsp, shredded red pepper, whole sesame seeds 
						</td>
					</tr>	
